comment: Sloan (BKN) sets the screen on Drummond (DET) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Drummond (DET) and Lopez (BKN) briefly engage and separate while looking to establish post position.

Sloan (BKN) steps OOB while in possession of the ball.
Jackson (DET) and Sloan (BKN) make incidental contact with one another during the drive into the paint.
Sloan (BKN) makes contact with Jackson (DET) that affects his RSBQ at the start of the drive.
Ilyasova (DET) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Larkin (BKN) that does not affect his driving layup attempt.
Lopez (BKN) pushes Drummond (DET) affecting his ability to set the screen.
Larkin (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position on the driving shot attempt by Jackson (DET).
